description: JSON Data about a single attachment.

tokenId.description: This token is used to get a pre-signed URL that can be used to download this attachment.

previewId.description: This token is used to get a pre-signed URL that can be used to download this attachment's preview.

url.description: When provided, the URL can be used to directly download this attachment.

previewState.description: The state of the preview for this attachment
previewState.name: PreviewState
